name: December 'Heart To Heart' Tour Bundle - Liverpool - The Lantern Theatre - Dec 1st
description:
DECEMBER 'HEART TO HEART' TOUR

**To buy more than one ticket in one purchase just keep adding the tickets to your basket and then proceed to checkout**

I'm excited to announce my 'Heart To Heart' Tour in December! This will be a chance to chat and chill out with me whilst I play you my songs in an intimate setting. It's going to have a personal vibe as I want to you to ask me questions, chat with me and generally get to know me better.

Tickets are really limited so you'll need to grab yours whilst you can!

This intimate experience with Mike includes:

-Limited edition ticket-
-Exclusive unplugged 6 track EP-
-Heart To Heart tour wrist band-
-Signed post card with all venue info-
-Meet & greet-

Ticket & bundle will be sent to you in the post.

Doors: 7pm, Curfew: 10pm

Tickets: 15 pounds

Terms and conditions can be found on www.mikedignam.com/tour
